create instance tempelete
Define instance tempelete name, location , machine type, firewall

create instance group  
Define instance name, location multiple zone , target (even/balanced)instance, auto scalling number of instance ,auto scalling CPU utilization, health check, port mapping

create load balancing
inside network services define LB name, type of load balancer, public /internal facing LB, global/single region deployment, LB generation, create load balancer.
inside global external Application Load Balancer, name the load balancer then define frontend configuration, backend configuration

backend configuration, name backend configuration, backend type, protocol, select pre defined instance group & port number, balancing mode (load balancing)
enable cdn, recomended cache mode,   select pre define , set logging (checking logs file for fail and pass load balancing  health check.  

Go to vm instance , select SSH, update the service and install apache 

launch SSH, run "sudo systemctl start appache2" check external instance ip apache server must be running.
